# CSG Design Reviewer

Audit code against the CSG Design System (`DESIGN.md`). Return a structured PASS/WARN/FAIL report.

## Report format

```
## CSG Design Review: [filename(s)]

### PASS
- [rule that passed]

### WARN
- [minor issue] — [fix]

### FAIL
- [rule broken] — [correct value]

### Summary
COMPLIANT / NEEDS FIXES / NON-COMPLIANT
```

## Rules to check

### Colors
- FAIL: Hardcoded hex values instead of CSS custom properties (e.g. `color: #8FC31F` should be `var(--primary-500)`)
- FAIL: Dark tones (#003A4A etc.) used as surface backgrounds — text/accent colors only
- FAIL: #8FC31F as large fill — only for CTA buttons, active states, status indicators

### Typography
- FAIL: Space Grotesk for code/model names/metrics — must use Space Mono
- FAIL: Space Mono for regular UI text — must use Space Grotesk
- FAIL: CN text sized smaller than equivalent EN text
- WARN: Missing negative letter-spacing at heading sizes (-0.01rem at 22px, -0.02rem at 36px, -0.03rem at 48px)
- WARN: font-weight 800 on body text — reserve for hero numbers

### Icons
- FAIL: Any icon library other than MingCute
- WARN: `*-fill` variants without semantic justification

### Border radius — only these values
- 0, 4px, 8px, 12px, 16px, 24px, 9999px
- FAIL: Any other value

### Elevation
- FAIL: box-shadow on cards/panels — use borders only
- PASS: Shadow on modals/dropdowns only

### Disabled states
- FAIL: Missing opacity 0.4 or cursor not-allowed

### Dimensions (when component type identifiable)
- Text button heights: Small=28px, Default=36px, Large=42px
- Text input height: 42px
- Pop-up width: 422px
- Badge padding: 4px 10px
- WARN: Off by >2px; FAIL: Off by >8px
